shiyun-corpus — licensing

This repository contains TWO kinds of material with DIFFERENT terms:

1. ORIGINAL WORK of this project — the build/validation scripts (scripts/**),
   the curated annotations and corrections (curated/**), the schema, and the
   documentation — is released under the MIT License (below).

2. POEM TEXT DATA (data/**) is aggregated from upstream parent corpora and is
   NOT uniformly MIT. Each record carries a `provenance.license` field. Classical
   texts in data/ are public-domain (PD). Modern / in-copyright material is kept
   separately under data/_restricted/ and is NOT covered by the MIT grant below;
   see SOURCES.md for the per-source terms (Werneror MIT-tooling/PD-text,
   yuxqiu Apache-2.0, sheepzh non-commercial). Respect each upstream's license.

